title: The Almighty Jacobe-stradamus sees the future!
description:
J&J's NBA Previews roll on, this time with the appearance of the all-knowing, all-ecompassing Jacobe-stradamus! He's here to give you a glimpse at the future of this NBA Season, and he sees some pretty wild s***! A 3-time MVP, LaVar vs MJ Beef! A stunning 1st round KO and much, much more! Plus, Ben Simmons reminds fans that he really bring some elite skills to the table, the Dolphins quit ping pong, and we get a caller who can't remember if he's called before... pull up! Medicinal!
